14.000Z","msg":"覺得暫時人生中睇過嘅戲都冇一套接近有interstellar 咁好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:41:12.000Z","msg":"Interstellar 真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但打仗個套真係睇到屌老母"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:42:07.000Z","msg":"Dunkirk我覺得唔算好睇又唔算難睇<br />\n係一套好真實嘅戲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T15:08:39.000Z","msg":"唔係差<br />\n但唔深刻"},{"pid":"46af36d510a7efdadfbbefc7a0578b306abb6661","tid":995954,"uid":60635,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T15:25:17.000Z","msg":"我同意，入場睇幾套interstellar堅失望。我基本唔睇太空戲都覺得情節熟口熟面，上太空之後真係好悶。<br />\n<br />\n不過都唔夠batman3 失望，最尾兩條友都唔做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDunkirk 幾好，我自己去過果個城市同海岸，還原得唔錯。海陸空戰線最後連慣到一齊都收得唔錯，個機師過度神化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：入場睇過batman 2，睇戲剩係娛樂。"},{"pid":"2a51cdd67e24d6b3a35352c6c5fa7afa2055da3a","tid":995954,"uid":7262,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T15:54:30.000Z","msg":"Interstellar ，Dunkirk <br />\n真係唔識欣賞<br />\n<br />\nThe dark knight rises <br />\n依套最後真係好撚失望，趕收尾<br />\nBatman 同Bane對打戲實在太柒 <br />\nBane突然智障 輸得好兒戲<br />\n呢套好遺憾"},{"pid":"72ca86bcb754131d25c3be54aa87f17012167840","tid":995954,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T17:13:31.000Z","msg":"笑片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n災難片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n恐怖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9591e2e70cc38274d0b14fc5e85aa740abadd47","tid":995954,"uid":104640,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"等睇又唔知做乜鳩唒一大舊錢去搭個景，用佢兩分鐘就算。明明cg做到又要話追求真實去呃曝光。屌你封撚左條華爾街炸撚埋架大車講撚到好有追求咁，人地《狂野時速》咁撚大場面都冇你咁大陣仗。又懶係野咁用imax菲林吖，實景拍火星地理吖，實景五維空間，講出嚟都覺得on99。淨係識靠個細佬同燒銀紙。明明可以做得更好，不過淨係識睇票房做人，同史匹堡一鳩樣。俾翻大學嗰陣拍《following 》個nolan我得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c95fdbdc786ee29908005d2a703e70cbae49e4","tid":995954,"uid":123733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"11e8a2a266e173442c86023134f81e2262541990","tid":995954,"uid":49247,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"dde89fe3852e08c18a04ab08bf46431b3a38dbfe","tid":995954,"uid":22839,"like":5,"dislike":32,"score":-27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:44:54.000Z","msg":"Nolan最撚廢係Interstellar咁濟, 僅始於Batman III<br />\n話最好睇一定係細蚊仔"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"未見過大蛇屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n排Prestige, Dark Knight都未到佢啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T17:39:25.000Z","msg":"我第一次見人話The Prestige廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我睇過七八次起碼"},{"pid":"cff02b22dac3ae75559ab47fcb21d78cd0891442","tid":995954,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11e8a2a266e173442c86023134f81e2262541990","tid":995954,"uid":49247,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"dde89fe3852e08c18a04ab08bf46431b3a38dbfe","tid":995954,"uid":22839,"like":5,"dislike":32,"score":-27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:44:54.000Z","msg":"Nolan最撚廢係Interstellar咁濟, 僅始於Batman III<br />\n話最好睇一定係細蚊仔"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"未見過大蛇屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n排Prestige, Dark Knight都未到佢啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T18:24:34.000Z","msg":"最廢一定係insomia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331c2c1b6a9686addf9cbed7fd6b2a900812c713","ti